{"tid":2390412,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"210201 「強制檢測大廈名單監察」暫停更新","createTime":"2021-02-01T13:48:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T08:30:41.000Z","uid":51754,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2e5b14688f56f867089d3fca8236215f63b4013a","tid":2390412,"uid":51754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T13:48:42.000Z","msg":"港共1晚突襲封4區 禁足尖嘴油麻地紅磡元朗住宅<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210201/SWPIR4BZRRGHDDAW3MFOY46V34/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210201%2FSWPIR4BZRRGHDDAW3MFOY46V34%2F&d=FyOxfEvlGqeE3CGJWKQQlwpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=585e464b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210201%2FSWPIR4BZRRGHDDAW3MFOY46V34%2F&h=26a4310e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210201/SWPIR4BZRRGHDDAW3MFOY46V34/</a><br />\n<br />\n港共今日指明，即日起一切冇源頭確診大廈都會強制撩鼻。<br />\n張建宗做埋<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\"> 犯 罪 預 告 </span></span></strong>，<br />\n講明「未來10日會更頻密快閃封區」，<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">即晚就封 4 區大廈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>去到呢個時候，再跟住名單逐個檢查報告返係唔係符合準則，已經再冇意義，<br />\n因為所謂準則任佢朝令夕改，從來都係</strong><strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\"> 防 民 甚 於 防 疫 </span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>所以，「強制檢測大廈名單監察」會即晚起暫停更新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n改為不定期按需要出Post反對偽防疫真濫權惡行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n繼續做好個人衞生之餘，<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"green\">反對任意封區，<br />\n對抗政府濫權，<br />\n先係香港抗疫唯一出路。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n過往資料:<br />\n210131 今日名單又有出錯 / 廟街封完又中 / 麗港城兩座受災 / 預測下次封樓<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2389593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2389593</a><br />\n<br />\n210130 新增 1 街區 + 0 大廈 (+ 1 地盤) <a href=\"https://lih.kg/2388030\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2388030</a><br />\n210129 新增 0 街區 + 5 大廈 (+ 1 地盤) <a href=\"https://lih.kg/2387138\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2387138</a><br />\n210128 新增 0 街區 + 1 大廈 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/2385354\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2385354</a><br />\n210127 新增 1 街區 + 11 大廈 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/gBEruT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gBEruT</a><br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">↳↳↳峰華邨曉峰樓翻閹理據不足</span></strong><br />\n210126 新增 3 街區 + 7 大廈 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/gBtJjT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gBtJjT</a><br />\n210125 新增 1 街區 + 4 大廈 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/gBkkmT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gBkkmT</a><br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">↳↳↳深夜開始推行街區鳩驗污水</span></strong><br />\n210124 新增 4 座大廈 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/gANtRT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gANtRT</a><br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">↳↳↳仁石樓二次檢測原因不清</span></strong>"},{"pid":"adf0e029a54a656588180a10d1e3fcc2b47b6939","tid":2390412,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T13:51:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfb342edd7efece95ed0e957a00a414a8ab71480","tid":2390412,"uid":247896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T13:53:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmo